video.title: Power Rangers Operation Overdrive
video.synopsis: To keep powerful jewels from falling into the hands of two wicked brothers, five young Power Rangers set out on a dangerous global adventure.

episodes.synopsis: Billionaire treasure hunter Andrew Hartford finds the ancient Corona Aurora. But in the process, he unknowingly awakens two warring alien brothers.
episodes.title: Kick into Overdrive: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: Hartford is kidnapped by Moltor, who also steals the Corona Aurora. Mack must prove himself as the Red Ranger and aid the team in saving his father.
episodes.title: Kick into Overdrive: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Will's self-reliance causes friction within the team. The Rangers seek one of the Corona Aurora gems in the underwater ruins of Atlantis.
episodes.title: The Underwater World

episodes.synopsis: Dax rescues a girl named Mira from a monster attack and they quickly become a couple.
episodes.title: Heart of Blue

episodes.synopsis: After putting a bystander in jeopardy, Mack doesn't feel he's cut out to be a Ranger.
episodes.title: Weather or Not

episodes.synopsis: Searching the island of St. Lucia for the first jewel of the Corona Aurora, the Rangers stumble upon the ghost of Brownbeard, the pirate.
episodes.title: Pirate in Pink

episodes.synopsis: Ronny's competitive nature begins to annoy her teammates. Will things get worse when she butts heads with Mack over first usage of the latest weapon?
episodes.title: At All Cost

episodes.synopsis: Will is fired by Hartford for selling Zord tech on the side! Taking his Tracker with him, the Black Ranger joins up with Miratrix.
episodes.title: Both Sides Now

episodes.synopsis: Flurious and Moltor put aside their sibling rivalry and combine forces against the Rangers.
episodes.title: Follow the Ranger

episodes.synopsis: Dax gets his big break as an actor, but Mr. Hartford refuses to allow him to take the role, since it may conflict with his Ranger duties.
episodes.title: Lights, Camera, Dax

episodes.synopsis: The Rangers visit Rose's college in London to try to get the parchment deciphered, only to lose it to Tyzonn, Moltor's latest alien lizard henchman.
episodes.title: Face to Face: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: Mack joins forces with Tyzonn, learning that the reptilian creature is actually a human from the planet Mercury, cursed by Moltor.
episodes.title: Face to Face, Part 2

episodes.synopsis: The search for the next jewel leads the Rangers to Portugal and then to Brazil, with a new group of villains always one step ahead of them!
episodes.title: Man of Mercury: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: It's up to Mr. Hartford to restore the liquidized Tyzonn to his human form.
episodes.title: Man of Mercury: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Tyzonn gets trapped between his human and mercury forms! Can he be saved in time to aid the Rangers against the Giant Robot-piloting Fearcats?
episodes.title: Behind the Scenes

episodes.synopsis: Will attempts to teach Tyzonn how to blend in on Earth, but when the Mercurian starts to copy Will a little too closely, they clash.
episodes.title: Just Like Me

episodes.synopsis: With the Cannon of Ki Amuk and Mjolnir in their possession, the Rangers track the next clue to Mexico.
episodes.title: It's Hammer Time

episodes.synopsis: Having swiped the Paedra Aztec Del Compass from the Rangers, Moltor puts it in the possession of his old friend Blothgaar.
episodes.title: Out of Luck

episodes.synopsis: Using the compass, the Rangers finally find the Third Jewel of the Corona Aurora.
episodes.title: One Gets Away

episodes.synopsis: The son of Lord Zedd and Rita Repulsa, Thrax, unites all four Corona Aurora-seeking factions of villains into a new Evil Alliance.
episodes.title: Once a Ranger: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: No longer having Ranger powers, the former Overdrive Rangers return to their civilian lives.
episodes.title: Once a Ranger: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: The Rangers get a day off and plan a relaxing picnic in the forest. Unfortunately for Rose, Tyzonn is obsessed with getting to know her better.
episodes.title: One Fine Day

episodes.synopsis: Ronny runs into a stubborn obstacle named Will while trying to throw a Halloween party.
episodes.title: Ronny on Empty: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: Norg and Will strike up a strange alliance in their attempt to find the Fearcats' secret hideout.
episodes.title: Ronny on Empty: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: While battling one of Kamdor's monsters, the Rangers get their computer systems infected with a virus.
episodes.title: Things Not Said

episodes.synopsis: After learning about his true robotic nature, Mack starts to go through an identity crisis.
episodes.title: Red Ranger Unplugged

episodes.synopsis: Mig and Benglo utilize the power of the Octavian Chalice and unleash the mighty Agrios, a giant robotic creature.
episodes.title: Home and Away: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: While the other Rangers continue to be outmatched by the Fearcats and Agrios, Tyzonn begins to accept his fiancée's claims that he never was a Ranger.
episodes.title: Home and Away: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Using Mack's internal CPU to review their Ranger careers, the team takes the time to refresh their memories as to who has which Corona Aurora jewel.
episodes.title: Way Back When

episodes.synopsis: Using the Octavian Chalice, the Rangers journey to Greece in an attempt to find the next jewel via an ancient ritual.
episodes.title: Two Fallen Foes

episodes.synopsis: The Rangers return to Egypt and then travel to Japan in their heated quest to find the key to unlock the last hidden jewel.
episodes.title: Nothing to Lose

episodes.synopsis: With the ultimate power of the completed Corona Aurora at his disposal, Flurious freezes all of San Angeles and prepares to conquer the world.
episodes.title: Crown and Punishment
